item.title: Notes on Notes
item.description: Notes for iOS and MacOS is better than I remembered… even if the last vestige of the opulaent skeumorphism remains.

item.title: Agenda
item.description: Agenda is a productivity app that boasts a distinctive visual style that is hard to ignore. It’s effectively a note-taking app, of which there are many for both the Mac and iOS, but some core features distinguish it from this crowded field.
